Package danfulea.db

Provides the classes necessary to handle database related operations.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DatabaseAgent
    The DatabaseAgent class handles basic database operations: connection, creation or removal of database and tables, select to retrieve database data in form of data and column names vectors, insert, delete and update data into tables.
    DatabaseAgentSupport
    This class extends the functionality of the core DatabaseAgent.
    SimpleTableModel
    Simple table model for the database viewer, which is a JTable object.
    TestClass
    Test Class for database operation.

Package danfulea.db Description

Provides the classes necessary to handle database related operations.

It uses standard JDBC technology.

Version:
3.0
Author:
Dan Fulea
